<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٣ - <span class="c2">(٢٥٩١)</span> حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5605">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ رَافِعٍ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3185">وَعَبْدُ بْنُ حُمَيْدٍ </a>كِلَاهُمَا عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3447">عَبْدِ الرَّزَّاقِ </a>،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6279">مَعْمَرٌ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5936">ابْنِ الْمُنْكَدِرِ </a>فِي هَذَا الْإِسْنَادِ مِثْلَ مَعْنَاهُ،<span class="c5"> غَيْرَ أَنَّهُ قَالَ:</span> بِئْسَ أَخُو الْقَوْمِ وَابْنُ الْعَشِيرَةِ .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>